snippet.title: My Lovely Cat(Prologue)
snippet.description: Hope you guys enjoyed this little video it was on a short notice so it isn't that good but if you want me to continue in a root leave it down in the comments if you want one of the characters. The only people I can't officially date are the manager and Shiro so you can't ask for them you can ask for any other Kitty though. Examples Leo, Rin, Sora, Nora are the only ones available right now. Put which one you want me to do first!
